extends DroolsConnectorMetadataAdapter
implements org.mule.api.context.MuleContextAware, org.mule.api.lifecycle.Disposable, org.mule.api.lifecycle.Initialisable, org.mule.api.lifecycle.Startable, org.mule.api.lifecycle.Stoppable
    A DroolsConnectorLifecycleInjectionAdapter is a wrapper around DroolsConnector that adds lifecycle methods to the pojo. This adapter also allows the injection of several Mule facilities when a MuleContext is set.
